This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the LLM360 organization:
- LLM360/Amber tokenizer.json (same tokenizer family as Snowflake/snowflake-arctic-base)
- LLM360/AmberChat tokenizer.json (same tokenizer family as Snowflake/snowflake-arctic-base)
- LLM360/Crystal tokenizer.json
- LLM360/CrystalChat tokenizer.json (same tokenizer family as LLM360/Crystal)
- LLM360/K2 tokenizer.json
- LLM360/K2-Chat tokenizer.json
- LLM360/K2-Think tokenizer.json (same tokenizer family as XiaomiMiMo/MiMo-7B-RL-0530)
- LLM360/K2-Think-V2 tokenizer.json

